	* templates/lighttpd/lighttpd-lxrserver.conf:
	  templates/lighttpd/lighttpd-lxrserver.conf: fix automatic
	  configuration for standard cases

	  Macro expansion tuned for the "classic" cases handled by
	  interactive configurator

2013-01-22 09:15  ajlittoz

	* templates/lighttpd/lighttpd-lxrserver.conf:
	  templates/lighttpd/lighttpd-lxrserver.cong: discrepancy between
	  config and script lighttpd-init

	  Script lighttpd-init puts/gets everything into/from
	  /var/run/lighttpd, notably the pid file, while
	  lighttpd-lxrserver.conf defines the state directory as /var/run
	  resulting in the pid file created in a different location. Fixed
	  by changing var.state_dir

