2012-11-21 15:04  ajlittoz

	* ident: ident: case-insensitive identifier search

	  Add a second query in so-called "case-insensitive" mode and merge
	  results with normal query. Line numbers for second query (unique
	  results only) are set negative to indicate approximate match.

