	  graphics file

	  Fix for bug #3587475: put parentheses around configuration
	  parameter in pattern

2012-11-21 13:33  ajlittoz

	* genxref: genxref: protect call to getfilehandle

	  Swish-e search cache needs a copy of source file, which is
	  obtained through getfilehandle. Check return value is defined
	  before using it!

