2012-11-14 17:24  ajlittoz

	* search: search: wrong file designation for sub checkvalidref

	  Search engines return OS-relative file paths while LXR expects
	  all paths starting with /(to easily catenate the file path --
	  relative to 'sourceroot' -- to the URL.

	  Simultaneously, fix coding style to be consistent across all
	  modules.

