	  File::Path added for make_path()

2012-09-29 19:05  ajlittoz

	* scripts/: configure-lxr.pl, recreatedb.pl: configure-lxr.pl,
	  recreatedb.pl: fix revision number display

	  $Revision: erroneously substituted twice because of double
	  recognition by CVS; proceed in two steps: remove first "Revision
	  ...", then initial dollar so that CVS does not see $Revision.

