2012-07-20 11:47  ajlittoz

	* genxref: genxref: Bad swish-e handling

	  Typo (swhish instead of swish) preventing detection of swish-e
	  executable.  Missing space between options when invoking swish-e.

2012-05-04 08:14  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Config.pm: Config.pm: new 'glimpsedirbase' and
	  'swishdirbase' parameters

	  To ease lxr.conf configuration, 'glimpsedir' and 'swishdir' can
	  now be dynamically computed as catenation of '*dirbase' and
	  'virtroot' (since virtual roots are unique).	_ensuredirexists
	  modified to behave like mkdir -p (to avoid dependency on
	  File::Path)

2012-04-20 19:56  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Common.pm: egg-and-hen problem

	  clean_release needs $pathname to check for an existing release
	  and fix_paths needs and initialised $releaseid to determine the
	  correct nature of $pathname (file or directory). To break the
	  vicious circle, clean_release is computed first with a raw path
	  from the URL and $pathname is subsequently canonised with a
	  correct $releaseid.

2012-04-19 11:40  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/: Files.pm, Files/BK.pm, Files/CVS.pm, Files/GIT.pm,
	  Files/Plain.pm: Files.pm and Files/*.pm: commenting, reorganizing
	  source

	  Support for Git fixed; main changes blindly ported to BK.pm but
	  not tested

