	* templates/Apache/apache-lxrserver.conf:
	  templates/Apache/apache-lxrserver.conf

	  Fix for bug #3159397: spurious caret ^ on Alias directive makes
	  confusion with AliasMatch. Some distros reject the directive;
	  others, more permissive, accept it. Illegal caret removed.

