	  call to fixpaths in httpinit after check for variable 'v'.

2012-04-14 07:57  ajlittoz

	* search: search: glimpse search denied under some distributions

	  The "positive" file filter pattern is not always accepted. It is
	  replaced by a "negative" pattern preceded by -v option which
	  seems to be more generally accepted.

