2012-04-02 19:01  ajlittoz

	* scripts/: ANSI-escape.sh, initial-config.sh:
	  scripts/initial-config.sh

	  Fix for bug #3514226: templates directory xas left with
	  permission r-- instead of r-x Also, make sure lixrconf.d
	  directory does exist; create ANSI-escape.sh to common factor ANSI
	  color highlighting sequences

2012-03-29 19:55  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang/generic.conf: generic.cong: improve Perl support

	  Minor adjustment for a better identification of comments

2012-03-29 18:58  ajlittoz

	* diff, lib/LXR/Files.pm, lib/LXR/Tagger.pm, lib/LXR/Files/BK.pm,
	  lib/LXR/Files/CVS.pm, lib/LXR/Files/Plain.pm: diff, Tagger.pm,
	  Files.pm, Plain.pm, CVS.pm, BK.pm: fix for bug #2714744 "Tagger &
	  Plain inefficient"

	  When files need to be handed over to an external tool, a
	  temporary copy was made and the tool operated in this copy. In
	  the case of plain files, this is inefficient since the file is
	  already available in the tree.  Method tmpfile changed to
	  realfilename where the name of the plain file is returned or the
	  name of the copy. New method releaserealfilename is called when
	  the file is no longer needed. This does nothing for plain files
	  and deletes temp copy otherwise.  Notes: 1- Git.pm not updated
	  because support is broken in CPAN.	     2- BK.pm blindly
	  updated by guess (current maintainer has no BK copy nor
	  experience).

2012-03-29 13:43  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXRversion.pm: LXRversion.pm: more automation in release
	  procedure

	  "Constant" LXRversion automatically configured by script
	  makerelease.pl during releasing procedure (it was too easy and
	  too frequent to forget it) *** This requires a modified
	  makerelease.pl which is not yet checked in ***

