	* doc/INSTALL-0.11: doc/INSTALL-0.11

	  Correct a confusion between Perl and ctags minimal versions

2012-03-27 16:48  ajlittoz

	* diff, lib/LXR/Common.pm, lib/LXR/Template.pm,
	  templates/html/html-head-btn-smaller.html,
	  templates/html/html-head-btn.html: diff, Common.pm, Template.pm,
	  templates/*btn*: redesign the way included (and potentially
	  included) files are handled so that a change in the variables
	  environment leads to a recomputation of the filename.

	  This change also allows to compare (diff) two files differing by
	  not just the 'v' (version) variable.

