	  comment Config.pm

2012-03-27 09:12  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang/generic.conf: generic.conf: improve Perl support

	  Add "special" notation $#x for array length to prevent switching
	  to comment region.

2012-03-27 08:59  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Common.pm: sub urlargs

	  Change query string argument separator from ; to &. W3C standard
	  says they are equivalent but ';' leads to HTTP 403 error if
	  string is too long (about 110 chars.) on some servers.

