2012-01-29 15:35  ajlittoz

	* search: search: fix for bug #1183103 (0 search result when max
	  number reached before file-name match)

	  Moved filename filtering in glimpse result collecting loop
	  (instead of stuffing all results up to maxhits, then filtering
	  when editing). Now, filter when collecting, then edit.

