	* scripts/lighttpd-init: New script lighttpd-init for start-,
	  stop-, reload-ing lighttpd server

2012-01-29 07:38  ajlittoz

	* templates/lighttpd/: lighttpd-lxr-modules.conf,
	  lighttpd-lxrserver.conf: Experimental support for lighttpd web
	  server

	  To allow simultaneous service on Apache and lighttpd, port is no
	  longer considered when trying to match host-name. However, it
	  must still be written in URL.

	  templates/lighttpd/ created to hold lighttpd related templates

2012-01-29 07:36  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Config.pm, lib/LXR/Template.pm,
	  scripts/initial-config.sh,
	  templates/Apache/apache-lxrserver.conf,
	  templates/Apache/htaccess-generic,
	  templates/Apache/lxrserver.conf: Experimental support for
	  lighttpd web server

	  To allow simultaneous service on Apache and lighttpd, port is no
	  longer considered when trying to match host-name. However, it
	  must still be written in URL.

2012-01-29 07:24  ajlittoz

	* LXRimages/LXRlogo32.ico, LXRimages/LXRlogo64.jpeg,
	  LXRimages/valid-html401.png, LXRimages/vcss.gif,
	  templates/html/html-head-btn-smaller.html,
	  templates/html/html-head-btn.html,
	  templates/html/html-head-smaller.html,
	  templates/html/html-head.html, templates/html/html-tail.html:
	  Image designation using HTML-absolute form in templates to ease
	  integration in existing web-sites when DocumentRoot is not equal
	  to LXR root directory.

	  Directory images renamed LXRimages to remove potential conflict
	  with Apache's /images

2012-01-29 07:10  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Common.pm: when forcing a variable value,
	  dollar sigil not stripped from argument causing variable not
	  updated; $releaseid was set too late, preventing file
	  identificatoin and path transformation (setting moved before
	  include file path handling)

2012-01-26 17:22  ajlittoz

	* genxref, lib/LXR/Lang/Generic.pm: Generic.pm: replaced a regexp
	  with 5.10 syntax by a 5.8 syntax one, so that it will compile
	  with older Perl interpreter (subsequent processing is ugly!)
	  genxref updated not to fail on this dependency

2012-01-26 16:35  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/: Lang.pm, Lang/Generic.pm, Lang/Perl.pm, Lang/Ruby.pm,
	  Lang/generic.conf: Rearchitect the language handlers: Generic.pm
	  is becoming too big, trying to cope with an excessive number of
	  languages.  Created Perl.pm and Ruby.pm; Generic.pm concentrates
	  now on C family generic.conf updated for Ruby.

2012-01-25 21:03  ajlittoz

	* templates/lxr.css: templates/lxr.css: styles for links to fast
	  switch to other trees (used in html-head-*)

2012-01-25 17:29  ajlittoz

	* genxref, source, lib/LXR/Common.pm, lib/LXR/Index.pm,
	  lib/LXR/Tagger.pm, lib/LXR/Files/CVS.pm, lib/LXR/Index/Mysql.pm,
	  lib/LXR/Index/Oracle.pm, lib/LXR/Index/Postgres.pm,
	  templates/lxr.css: CVS management: source file retrieval in side
	  branches and automatic version enumeration

	  This fix involves many source files and subs, mainly in CVS.pm
	  and genxref. The main task is to scan the CVS header to extract
	  all tags and release numbers and to apply a new algorithm in
	  parsecvs sub to reconstruct the target file.

	  genxref --allversions in CVS mode purges all DB tables. This
	  necessitates a new method 'purgeall' in Files.pm (existent
	  purge() operates on a single designated releaseid and we have no
	  exhaustive list of releases for a CVS repository). This method
	  has been tested for MySQL and copied as is in Oracle.pm and
	  Postgres.pm. Testers welcome.

	  As a bonus, annotation display has been enhanced with background
	  highlighting of latest addition to repository.

2012-01-23 10:06  ajlittoz

	* scripts/: initdb-config.sh, initial-config.sh: scripts/*: a
	  dollar sign was not escaped in a shell command (previous commit
	  ineffective)

