	  preparation step if source-tree rests in an SCM, since the engine
	  does not understand the SCM file format and won't do any useful
	  work anyway.

2012-01-04 19:43  ajlittoz

	* genxref: genxref: correction for bug 3469081 Tests for glimpse
	  and swish-e were independently trying to configure the dree-text
	  search engine to use, resulting in both defined if they existed
	  on the computer. Now, forcing a free-text search engine is
	  deferred until the user preference can be tested (after reading
	  the configuration).

