2011-12-21 18:18  ajlittoz

	* templates/: html-dir.html, html-fatal.html, html-head.html,
	  html-ident.html, html-search-glimpse.html, html-tail.html,
	  html-ident-refs.html: New design for the HTML templates
	  html-ident-refs.html now incorporated in html-ident.html (And
	  html-search-swish.html lagging a bit)

2011-12-21 18:10  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Markup.pm: Template.pm: new package from splitting
	  Common.pm becoming too large Contains all subs for markup of
	  files

2011-12-21 17:27  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Files/CVS.pm, diff, ident, search, source,
	  lib/LXR/Common.pm, lib/LXR/Template.pm: diff, ident, search,
	  source, Common.pm, Template.pm, CVS.pm: eliminate possible
	  collision between LXR-internal URL parameters and user "variable"
	  name

	  LXR-internal parameters are now prefixed with an underscore;
	  variable names can be arbitrary as long as they don't start with
	  an underscore (or dollar, which will be used to override user
	  variable value).  This new rule/restriction will be added to the
	  documentation.

2011-12-19 13:16  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Template.pm: Template.pm: added sub gettemplate to have
	  consistent error management and simplify template retrieval
	  Corrected also an error in template fallback for header and
	  footer (wrong test for existence)

