	* genxref, lib/LXR/Lang/Generic.pm: genxref, Generic.pm: moved
	  ctags version checking from Generic.pm to genxref because that
	  check caused problems on SourceForge where it is forbidden to
	  launch arbitrary programs from Web Service.

	  And it is where that test belongs since ctags is only used during
	  the indexing phase (under genxref responsability)

