2011-06-11 13:00  ajlittoz

	* CHANGES: Prepare release 0.9.10

2011-06-10 17:08  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Config.pm: Preparatory corrections for SCM management

	  Note: Perl complains on access to 'range' when it is defined as a
	  sub. It says "cannot use string $var as a hash ref while strict
	  refs in use". Expertise needed.

2011-06-10 15:48  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Untaint globally $ENV{'PATH'} with a safe(?)
	  content

2011-06-10 15:40  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Make correct links to README files

	  Use common sub fileref to create links to file and remove README
	  from further processing to avoid messing up the newly built HTML
	  tag.

2011-06-10 15:22  ajlittoz

	* Local.pm: Garantee sub dirdesc always returns a value

	  Return &nbsp; when dirdesc doesn't find a README file in the
	  listed directory instead of 'undef' so that CSS can decorate the
	  cell (without that content, the cell is deleted by most browsers)

2011-05-29 15:13  ajlittoz

	* LXRversion.pm: [no log message]

2011-05-29 14:59  ajlittoz

	* templates/html-dir.html: (Cosmetic) Changed GMT to UTC

	  GMT origin is at noon (solar time), while UTC origin is at
	  midnight (legal time) which is is the usual time origin for
	  ordinary human time.

2011-05-08 19:11  ajlittoz

	* Local.pm: Correct links in README markers

	  Transmit directory name of README file to sub descreadme and
	  desreadmehtml; generate links with fileref instead of reinventing
	  the wheel (with errors).

2011-05-08 16:49  ajlittoz

	* Local.pm: Use correct directory designation for marking items in
	  string

	  Argument $dir should be used instead of undefined hash %Path
	  (forgotten change many years back?)

2011-05-07 13:39  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Generate valid URI for graphic files display

	  To be handled by the web server, files need to be in the
	  "DocumentRoot" hierarchy. Provided there is a symbolic from LXR
	  root directory to source tree directory, it is possible to
	  generate a valid <img> tag to the file. Needs a new
	  'sourceaccess' parameter in lxr.conf.

2011-05-07 12:55  ajlittoz

	* diff: Allow variable width for left pane in diff

	  New feature: use value of config parameter 'diffleftwidth' for
	  number of characters in left pane. If not define, use 50
	  characters as was previously hard-coded

2011-04-21 07:44  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Modelink2button: make sure only </a> tag is
	  transformed

	  If only /a is transformed into closing button and form
	  delimiters, regexp erroneously targets filename starting with /a;
	  better to give full tag.

2011-04-14 18:00  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Global variable $pathname may be used before
	  being initialised causing display of bad version of file.  Shift
	  "cleaning" of query argument 'v' after cleaning query argument
	  'file' in httpinit

2011-04-08 19:13  ajlittoz

	* search: Untainting $ENV{'PATH'} forgotten for swishsearch way
	  back 1.22 (was done for glimpsesearch)

2011-04-08 16:00  ajlittoz

	* source, templates/lxr.conf: When in CVS mode, truncate the
	  annotation field to 16 characters to avoid line dangling. Signal
	  truncation with a *

2011-04-08 15:49  ajlittoz

	* ident: Debug feedback on idedntifier search limited to
	  definitions

	  Use our instead of my Don't display "references" title if
	  limitation on Configure with 0/1 instead of "true"/anything

	  Thanks to Martin Wilck

2011-04-07 08:35  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang/generic.conf: Correct string parsing

	  If escaping character appears as a litteral in last position of
	  string, it causes an "out-of-sync" condition. Correct "stay"
	  pattern must swallow ALL escaped characters.

2011-04-02 18:12  ajlittoz

	* ident, templates/lxr.conf: Search for identifier definition only

	  Did not test for 'true' value of parameter 'identfedonly' in
	  ident Added an example in lxr.conf

2011-04-02 15:39  ajlittoz

	* ident, templates/html-ident.html, templates/lxr.css: Offer the
	  possiblity to limit identifier search to definitions only

	  Add a check box in html-ident template and an hidden input field
	  to remember the state.  Add a config parameter for default check
	  at personal taste.  Add an "insertion" variable in printident to
	  check the box according to default state; when initialising
	  ident, define the check state as: - config parameter value if
	  first search - value of previous search for second+ so that user
	  does not have to (un)check again if he changed

2011-04-02 13:55  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Allow for easy modification of line number
	  width

	  In markupfile: pattern for @ltag adjusted so that line number may
	  have any width with a minimum of 3 digits. All that is needed is
	  to change $line above from $line = "001"; to $line = "00001"; to
	  get 5 digits. Interesting for files with more than 1000 lines to
	  prevent the colums from being ragged (if tree contains many of
	  these files).

2011-04-02 13:48  ajlittoz

	* diff, templates/lxr.css: Add background colors in diff markup

	  Colors for differing blocks can be adjusted with lxr.css

2011-04-02 11:40  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm, templates/diff-head-btn.html: State
	  information incorrect for diff with buttons-and-menus interface

	  Common.pm: needs to keep the state of variables when clicking on
	  a button to select a version to compare because the button value
	  is not transmitted as variable values but through diffvar and
	  diffval; the original version is described by the variables.
	  Corrected the diff-head-btn.html template in parallel

2011-04-02 09:52  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm, templates/diff-head-btn.html,
	  templates/html-head-btn.html: Allow for buttons-and-menus
	  interface

	  Add new HTML generating functions in Common.pm and provide
	  example templates

2011-03-28 14:12  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Extra space left instead of replacing by
	  zero-width space!

	  Space suppressed

2011-03-27 17:35  tag release-0-9-9

2011-03-27 17:35  ajlittoz

	* templates/lxr.conf, INSTALL: Simpler MySQL instructions

2011-03-27 15:54  ajlittoz

	* INSTALL, apache2-require.pl: Simplify installation - no change
	  needed in apache2-require.pl

	  Using relative paths (to LXR root directory), there is no need to
	  change apache2-require.pl during installation.  INSTALL changed
	  to reflect this.

