	* CHANGES, INSTALL: Prepare release 0.9.9

2011-03-27 07:29  ajlittoz

	* templates/lxr.conf: Forgot to remove parameter 'htmlfind'

2011-03-26 17:07  ajlittoz

	* robots.txt: Courtesy fencing against robots

	  Very restrictive robots.txt file prohibiting a well-behaved robot
	  from indexing the site.

2011-03-26 13:39  ajlittoz

	* templates/: html-dir.html, html-head.html: Template update

	  Related to more control with CSS

2011-03-26 13:33  ajlittoz

	* templates/html-find.html: Suppressed out-of-date files

	  notes: better information now in User's manual diff: replaced by
	  search, no longer integrated with Common.pm and others

2011-03-26 13:28  ajlittoz

	* notes, find: Suppressed out-of-date files

	  notes: better information now in User's manual diff: replaced by
	  search, no longer integrated with Common.pm and others

2011-03-26 13:22  ajlittoz

	* CREDITS.txt: Update and tribute to mbox

2011-03-26 13:19  ajlittoz

	* apache2-require.pl: Clarification on needed paths

	  apache2-require.pl contained 3 paths when only 2 are really
	  needed to load correctly LXR.

2011-03-26 13:15  ajlittoz

	* initdb-mysql: Remove duplicate index in initdb-mysql

2011-03-26 13:12  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang/generic.conf: Corrected typos

2011-03-26 13:06  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Replace space by zero-width space in banner

	  Real space splits the pathname only to allow the UA to wrap a
	  long pathname. Use now zero-width space (&#x200B;) for that (see
	  HTML standard).

2011-03-26 13:00  ajlittoz

	* LXRversion.pm, lib/LXR/Common.pm, templates/html-tail.html: New
	  template parameter: LXRversion

	  Allows to insert LXR release number in HTML footer or header

2011-03-26 12:45  ajlittoz

	* source, lib/LXR/Common.pm, templates/lxr.conf: Use pattern
	  'graphicfile' everywhere

	  To avoid inconsistency, pattern 'graphicfile' used now to select
	  a graphic file AND make LXR display it graphically.  Reduced the
	  pattern to file extension only.  Simplified extension matching in
	  fileicon.

2011-03-22 10:36  ajlittoz

	* templates/lxr.conf: Clarification about htmlhead and htmlfooter

	  Added a comment about the ability to use an operation-specific
	  header or footer by providing a xxxheader or xxxfooter HTML
	  parameter, wher xxx is one of source, sourcedir, diff, ident,
	  search

2011-03-22 08:41  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Removed typo in makefooter

	  Non edited copy-and-paste from makeheader: sourcedirhead was not
	  changed to sourcedirtail!

2011-03-20 15:00  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm, templates/lxr.conf, templates/lxr.css: Config
	  files restructuring

	  Corrected also typos and inaccuracies

2011-03-17 14:17  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang/Generic.pm: Added language-dependent include
	  handling

	  New feature: allow to transform the language-specific designation
	  of the include object to finally get a path to a file. Handling
	  is driven through new parameters in generic.conf language specs.

2011-03-17 10:29  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/: SimpleParse.pm, Lang/generic.conf: Improve language
	  parsing

	  Transform brute-force fragment splitting strategy into a more
	  state-oriented provessing. Only look for "open" delimiters. Then
	  accumulate until associated "end" delimiter only (not ALL
	  delimiters). Introduce "stay" delimiter to maintain context when
	  encountered.

	  Big impact on generic.conf which has been restructured at the
	  same occasion

2011-03-12 17:03  ajlittoz

	* templates/html-fatal.html, templates/lxr.conf, lib/LXR/Common.pm,
	  lib/LXR/Config.pm: Display error when tree not found

	  Display a configurable HTML page when a tree is not found instead
	  of die'ing silently leaving user with blank page or no change at
	  all

2011-03-12 16:39  ajlittoz

	* templates/lxr.conf: Added $Id to monitor changes

2011-03-12 16:37  ajlittoz

	* templates/lxr.conf: Reorganised lxr.conf into clearer sections
	  and subsections

2011-03-12 13:36  ajlittoz

	* source: Made generated HTML more XML compliant

	  Added </p> ro close <p> blocks

2011-03-12 13:10  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang.pm: Remove void comment marking at beginning of last
	  line in block

2011-03-12 13:05  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang.pm: Improve script recognition

	  If file has no known extension, try to see if is a #! script or
	  an emacs mode-tagged file.  Test only on the last element
	  (ignoring the eventual path)

2011-03-12 11:21  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang/Generic.pm: Make sure #directive is always
	  recognised

	  C and C++ allow to have spaces after #: ignore those spaces when
	  looking for the directive

2011-03-12 11:02  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/: Common.pm, Config.pm: Display nicely sources other than
	  iso-8859-1

	  Send an HTTP header with the character encoding to use Created a
	  new tree-specific parameter 'encoding' for the tree encoding

2011-03-12 10:24  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: No need of a jump link to itself on every line
	  number

	  Eliminate href=...#line-no from fileref return to make a "pure"
	  anchor definition with name=line-no

2011-03-12 10:06  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Correct graphic file processing

	  1. Parameter 'graphicfile' was not effective in pattern matching
	  (Perl undocumented limitation?) 2. Removed query string from
	  image display request link

2011-03-12 09:20  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang.pm: Eliminate rescan after marking for reserved word

	  If include file has a name similar to HTML tags and attributes
	  used for marking text, the tags themselves get marked after
	  reserved word processing.

	  Replace two-pass process with a single pass where identifier can
	  be routed to single handler according to its classification.

2011-03-12 08:33  ajlittoz

	* lib/LXR/Lang/Generic.pm: Eliminate rescan after marking for
	  reserved word

	  If user variable has a name similar to HTML tags and attributes
	  used for marking text, the tags themselves get marked after
	  reserved word processing.

	  Replace two-pass process with a single pass where identifier can
	  be routed to single handler according to its classification.

	  Simultaneously, made identifier recognition language dependent
	  (new parameter 'identdef' in generic.conf) with backward
	  compatible default

2011-03-11 21:15  ajlittoz

	* ident: Old interface leftover from DB revamping, upgraded to new
	  variable and function names

2010-01-15 23:23  tag release-0-9-8

2010-01-15 23:23  mbox

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Fix XSS exploit in title string

2010-01-05 18:00  tag release-0-9-7

2010-01-05 18:00  mbox

	* ident, search: Fix for CVE-2009-4497 from Dan Rosenberg

	  Avoid a XSS vulnerability

2010-01-05 17:59  mbox

	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Fix bug in clean_identifier

	  It wasn't cleaning the identifier properly, leaving a security
	  hole

2009-05-14 21:13  mbox

	* genxref, lib/LXR/Index.pm, lib/LXR/Index/DB.pm,
	  lib/LXR/Index/DBI.pm, lib/LXR/Index/Mysql.pm,
	  lib/LXR/Index/Oracle.pm, lib/LXR/Index/Postgres.pm: Remote
	  obsolete Index::DB backend that used NDBM storage.  Now only
	  Postgres, Mysql and Oracle are supported as backends.

	  Add a commit method to the Index interface that flushes a
	  transaction to disk and starts another one.  Added appropriate
	  calls from genxref to Index::commit

2009-05-10 11:54  adrianissott

	* Local.pm, diff, find, genxref, ident, initdb-mysql,
	  initdb-oracle.sql, initdb-postgres, search, source,
	  lib/LXR/Common.pm, lib/LXR/Files.pm, lib/LXR/Index.pm,
	  lib/LXR/Lang.pm, lib/LXR/Tagger.pm, lib/LXR/Files/BK.pm,
	  lib/LXR/Files/CVS.pm, lib/LXR/Files/GIT.pm,
