	* lib/LXR/Common.pm: Fix bug [ 1720862 ] Filename with space
	  reports does not exist

	  Add whitespace to allowed list of characters in pathname.

2009-03-23 16:41  mbox

	* .htaccess-apache2: Remove DirectoryIndex command as this caused
	  problems

2009-03-23 15:49  mbox

	* .htaccess, .htaccess-apache1, INSTALL: Created Apache 1.x version
	  of .htaccess for use with ModPerl1

	  Modified install instructions to match

2009-03-23 15:25  mbox

	* .htaccess-apache2: Updated to fix issues when running under
	  Modperl2 & Apache2:

	  - Change to RegistryPrefork so that working directory is the same
	  as the script directory rather than /.  This makes the template
	  inclusion work properly - Add DirectoryIndex to hide default
	  directory listing - Remove old mod_perl1 directives

2009-03-23 14:34  mbox

	* .htaccess_cgi: Set the handler for lxr.css to be the default
	  rather than a script.

	  Before this change, lxr.css was interpreted as a script due to
	  the ScriptAlias directive in httpd.conf.ew

2009-03-23 13:29  mbox

	* lib/LXR/Index/Mysql.pm: Fix bug [ 1645267 ] problem with MySQL
	  syntax in delete statement

	  Change MySQL delete statements as per bug report

