1999-12-25 21:58  pergj

	* genxref, ident, initdb-mysql, initdb-postgres, lib/LXR/Lang.pm,
	  lib/LXR/SimpleParse.pm, lib/LXR/Tagger.pm, lib/LXR/Index/DBI.pm,
